<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span><span class="c5">جثة الْإِنْسَان:</span> شخصه.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c5">وجثمانه:</span> جمَاعَة جِسْمه.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c5">وقمته:</span> أَعلَى رَأسه.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">والبشرة:</span> ظَاهر جلده كُله.<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c5">والأدمة:</span> بَاطِنه.<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c5">والفروة:</span> جلدَة الرَّأْس خَاصَّة.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c5">والقمحدوة:</span> الناشز من الرَّأْس فَوق الْقَفَا.<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span>والشؤون عروق فِي الرَّأْس مِنْهَا يجْرِي الدمع إِلَى الْعَينَيْنِ (وَيُقَال هِيَ ملتقى<a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>